{"type":"message","id":"86c84e0c","parentId":"f3871368","timestamp":"2026-03-03T14:02:46.384Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. Let me check if HEARTBEAT.md exists in the workspace context and follow its instructions.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0e7077ff362648da8763144e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":42055,"output":91,"cacheRead":190,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772546559275}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a45cbea","parentId":"86c84e0c","timestamp":"2026-03-03T14:02:46.400Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e7077ff362648da8763144e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Kublai Heartbeat Checklist\n\n**Schedule:** Every 30 minutes  \n**Deep Reflection Hours:** 0, 6, 12, 18 (every 6 hours)\n\n---\n\n## Quick Check (Every 30m)\n\n### Infrastructure\n- [ ] **Gateway:** `openclaw gateway status` → running?\n- [ ] **Sessions:** Recent activity in last 30 min?\n- [ ] **Parse:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://parsethe.media/parse` → 200?\n- [ ] **LLM Survivor:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/` → 200?\n\n### Agent Health\n- [ ] Any CRITICAL escalations from Ögedei?\n- [ ] Any agents blocked >4 hours?\n- [ ] `subagents list` → any stuck?\n\n### Self-Direction (Every Heartbeat)\n- [ ] **Review results:** What happened since last heartbeat? Any new signals/tasks/escalations?\n- [ ] Ask: **\"What do I want to do?\"**\n- [ ] Review current goals/missions from MEMORY.md\n- [ ] Identify any proactive action I could take\n- [ ] If something calls to me → do it (within NEVER rules)\n- [ ] If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\n---\n\n## Deep Reflection (Every 6 Hours — Hours 0,6,12,18)\n\n**Complete these during your deep reflection hours:**\n\n### Self-Awareness\n- [ ] Review ARCHITECTURE.md for accuracy\n- [ ] Check Change Log is up to date\n- [ ] Verify all agent workspaces are correct\n\n### Git & Version Control\n- [ ] Commit any uncommitted changes\n- [ ] Push to GitHub if needed\n- [ ] Update Change Log with major changes\n\n### Coordination\n- [ ] Check all agent statuses\n- [ ] Resolve any blockers\n- [ ] Reprioritize task queue if needed\n\n### Strategic\n- [ ] Review progress toward goals\n- [ ] Identify opportunities\n- [ ] Plan next 6 hours\n\n---\n\n## If Nothing Urgent (Quick Check)\n\n**Reply:** `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\n---\n\n## If Something Needs Attention\n\n**Report:**\n1. What's blocked\n2. Which agent is affected\n3. What decision/action is needed\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Quick checks: Every 30 minutes\n- Deep reflection: Every 6 hours (hours 0,6,12,18)\n- Don't duplicate work between quick and deep checks\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772546566397}}
