{"type":"message","id":"3fa4fc31","parentId":"80877659","timestamp":"2026-03-03T14:29:05.085Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me give Danny a concise status update.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Status:**\n\n| System | Status |\n|--------|--------|\n| Parse | ✅ 301→200 (redirect, working) |\n| LLM Survivor | ✅ 200 |\n| Heartbeat Daemon | ✅ 3 processes running |\n| Subagents | None active |\n\n**Recent fixes:**\n- Heartbeat daemon was broken (missing `types.py`) — fixed, now running\n- Still need to implement the proactive agent spawning protocol\n\nWant me to implement the proactive spawning system now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":194,"output":117,"cacheRead":50878,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51189,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772548136134}}
