{"type":"message","id":"e1189fc3","parentId":"dbd4d777","timestamp":"2026-03-03T14:53:19.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to implement a task queue system where:\n1. Tasks are written to agent-specific directories (temujin/tasks/, mongke/tasks/, etc.)\n2. Kublai decides which agent gets each task based on the routing matrix\n3. A consumer script picks up tasks and executes them\n\nLet me implement this system now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9680dee6bd464481b1393569","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/{temujin,mongke,chagatai,jochi,ogedei}/tasks"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":365,"output":203,"cacheRead":58878,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772549589305}}
