{"type":"message","id":"7782968c","parentId":"e8a0aa5b","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:54:44.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me identify issues:\n\n1. **mongke_quick_research** - Uses `mongke_gap_analysis` handler which does \"Analyze knowledge gaps daily\" - not the same as \"quick research on trending topics\". It's the wrong handler.\n\n2. **chagatai_content_generation** - Uses `chagatai_consolidate` handler which \"Consolidate reflections every 30 minutes (when idle)\" - not content generation.\n\nThese are mismatches - the handlers don't match the task names/descriptions. I should either:\n- Create proper new handlers\n- Or fix the registrations to use correct handlers\n\nLet me provide a critical review to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Critical Review - Issues Found:**\n\n| Task | Handler Used | Problem |\n|------|--------------|---------|\n| `mongke_quick_research` | `mongke_gap_analysis` | **Wrong handler** - analyzes knowledge gaps, not \"quick research on trending topics\" |\n| `chagatai_content_generation` | `chagatai_consolidate` | **Wrong handler** - consolidates reflections, not generates content |\n\n**Issues:**\n\n1. **Handler mismatch** - The mongke/chagatai tasks reuse existing handlers that don't match their purpose\n\n2. **temujin_task_pickup** - Works but runs external script which just logs (doesn't actually spawn agents)\n\n3. **temujin_code_review** - Requires Parse to be checked out at `/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github` - may fail silently\n\n**Recommendations:**\n\n1. Create proper handlers for mongke/chagatai OR remove the misleading tasks\n2. Enhance temujin_task_pickup to actually spawn agents via sessions_spawn\n3. Add fallback for temujin_code_review when Parse isn't checked out\n\nWant me to fix these issues now?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":453,"output":518,"cacheRead":77950,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772553245349}}
