egrated | Tasks marked executing but not spawned |\n\n**Summary:** Infrastructure is complete and working. The actual agent spawning integration (calling `sessions_spawn` from the handlers) needs to be wired up. Currently tasks flow through the system but don't trigger real agent execution.\n\nWant me to complete the spawning integration?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":99320,"output":750,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100070,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772553681538}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e79a2f5","parentId":"2ae660b7","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:02:11.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Implementation Status:**\n\n| Component | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| **Task Queue Infrastructure** | ✅ Complete | File-based queues for all 6 agents |\n| **Task Writer** | ✅ Complete | `task-queue-write.sh` working |\n| **Task Consumer** | ✅ Complete | Polls queues, marks tasks executing |\n| **Heartbeat Daemon** | ✅ Running | 19 tasks, all 6 agents |\n| **Proactive Spawning Protocol** | ✅ Documented | PROACTIVE-SPAWN-PROTOCOL.md |\n| **types.py Fix** | ✅ Complete | Heartbeat no longer crashes |\n\n**Gaps:**\n\n| Issue | Status | Impact |\n|-------|--------|--------|\n| `temujin_task_pickup` | ⚠️ Logs only | Doesn't actually spawn agents |\n| `mongke_quick_research` | ⚠️ Placeholder | Just logs, no real research |\n| `chagatai_content_generation` | ⚠️ Placeholder | Just logs, no content created |\n| Task consumer → agent spawn | ⚠️ Not integrated | Tasks marked executing but not spawned |\n\n**Summary:** Infrastructure is complete and working. The actual agent spawning integration (calling `sessions_spawn` from the handlers) needs to be wired up. Currently tasks flow through the system but don't trigger real agent execution.\n\nWant me to complete the spawning integration?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772553731615}}
