{"type":"message","id":"436a734f","parentId":"ad6b5f92","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:17:04.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent completed successfully and confirmed the spawning pipeline works. Now I can provide a complete status summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ Spawning Integration - COMPLETE AND VERIFIED**\n\n**Test Results:**\n\n| Component | Status | Evidence |\n|-----------|--------|----------|\n| Task Writer | ✅ | Created `high-1772554474.md` |\n| Heartbeat Pickup | ✅ | Logged \"Temujin spawn request queued\" |\n| Spawn Queue | ✅ | JSON written to `spawn-queue.jsonl` |\n| Spawn Consumer | ✅ | Created `temujin-1772554490.md` |\n| Agent Spawn (`sessions_spawn`) | ✅ | Subagent completed in 7.6s |\n| Result Auto-Announce | ✅ | Response returned without polling |\n\n**Subagent Response:**\n> \"The spawning pipeline is functional. I received the task context, processed it, and this response will be automatically reported back to the main agent.\"\n\n**Full Pipeline Working:**\n```\nTask → temujin/tasks/ → Heartbeat (every 15min) → spawn-queue.jsonl → \nspawn-consumer (cron) → spawn-requests/*.md → sessions_spawn → Agent executes → Auto-announce result\n```\n\n**Files Created:**\n- `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/spawn-consumer.sh`\n- `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/spawn-queue.jsonl`\n- `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/spawn-requests/`\n\n**Next Steps (Optional):**\n- Automate `sessions_spawn` calls for pending spawn requests (currently manual)\n- Add cleanup for processed spawn request files"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":106644,"output":404,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772554607695}}
