tonomously pick up tasks from a file queue. The other 5 agents:\n- Have heartbeat handlers (research, writing, testing, monitoring)\n- But **no task queues** to poll\n- Can't receive autonomous work assignments\n\n**To Fix:**\n\nAdd task pickup handlers for all agents:\n```\nmongke/tasks/     → mongke_task_pickup (every 15min)\nchagatai/tasks/   → chagatai_task_pickup (every 15min)\njochi/tasks/      → jochi_task_pickup (every 15min)\nogedei/tasks/     → ogedei_task_pickup (every 15min)\nkublai/tasks/     → kublai_task_pickup (every 5min)\n```\n\nThen Kublai can route chat messages to any agent's queue and they'll execute autonomously.\n\nWant me to add task pickup for all 6 agents?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":129534,"output":1047,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130581,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772558949846}}
