{"type":"message","id":"43363e22","parentId":"282a092f","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:48:29.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me provide a clean summary of what's complete.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ COMPLETE — Chat-to-Task System Fully Operational**\n\n**Final Architecture:**\n\n| Trigger | Flow | Latency |\n|---------|------|---------|\n| **Chat Message** | Kublai → `chat_to_task.handle_chat_task()` → `sessions_spawn` (immediate) | <10 sec |\n| **Heartbeat Task** | Agent task_pickup (5min) → spawn-pending.json → cron (2min) → `sessions_spawn` | ~7 min |\n\n**Files Created/Updated:**\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `chat_to_task.py` | Kublai's inline classifier + spawner |\n| `spawn-consumer.sh` | Cron processor for heartbeat spawns |\n| `spawn-pending.json` | Single queue for all spawns |\n\n**Usage for Kublai:**\n```python\nfrom chat_to_task import handle_chat_task\n\n# User says: \"Build a login feature\"\nresult = handle_chat_task(\"Build a login feature\")\n# → Call sessions_spawn with result[\"sessions_spawn_params\"]\n```\n\n**Tested:**\n- ✅ mongke-competitor-research spawned and executing\n- ✅ Queue processing verified\n- ✅ All 6 agents have task_pickup handlers"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":146559,"output":293,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146852,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772560104637}}
