{"type":"message","id":"7cec351d","parentId":"17b08bb1","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:58:29.210Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"08d2cce9-7c06-46e9-8911-5b152d7a875a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"sender\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 12:58 EST] implement:\n\nTask completion feedback (agent marks done when finished)\nRetry logic (3x before dead letter)\nContinuous task support (mode=\"session\" + heartbeat registration)"}],"timestamp":1772560709207}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d98e6e3","parentId":"7cec351d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:58:39.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to implement three features:\n1. Task completion feedback (agent marks done when finished)\n2. Retry logic (3x before dead letter)\n3. Continuous task support (mode=\"session\" + heartbeat registration)\n\nLet me implement these one by one:\n\n1. **Task completion feedback**: Need to update the spawn queue when an agent completes. This requires:\n   - Tracking which session corresponds to which spawn request\n   - When agent completes, update the queue status\n\n2. **Retry logic**: Need to track retries in the spawn request and re-queue failed tasks up to 3x\n\n3. **Continuous task support**: Add mode=\"session\" support and heartbeat registration for never-ending tasks\n\nLet me start implementing these features.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"I'll implement all three features now.\n\n## 1. Task Completion Feedback + Retry Logic\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a2a3411832554655ab0cd8db","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/chat_to_task.py","oldText":"def handle_chat_task(message, priority=\"normal\"):\n    \"\"\"\n    Full chat-to-task flow:\n    1. Classify message\n    2. Queue spawn request\n    3. Return params for sessions_spawn\n    \n    Kublai calls this, then calls sessions_spawn with returned params.\n    \"\"\"\n    classification = classify(message)\n    spawn_params = queue_spawn(classification, message, priority)\n    \n    return {\n        \"classified\": True,\n        \"agent\": classification[\"agent\"],\n        \"model\": classification[\"model\"],\n        \"label\": spawn_params[\"label\"],\n        \"task\": message.strip()[:200],\n        \"priority\": priority,\n        \"confidence\": round(classification[\"confidence\"], 2),\n        \"queued\": True,\n        \"ready_to_spawn\": True,\n        \"sessions_spawn_params\": {\n            \"task\": message.strip(),\n            \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n            \"label\": spawn_params[\"label\"],\n            \"model\": classification[\"model\"],\n            \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n        }\n    }","newText":"def handle_chat_task(message, priority=\"normal\", mode=\"run\", continuous=False):\n    \"\"\"\n    Full chat-to-task flow:\n    1. Classify message\n    2. Queue spawn request\n    3. Return params for sessions_spawn\n    \n    Kublai calls this, then calls sessions_spawn with returned params.\n    \n    Args:\n        mode: \"run\" (one-shot) or \"session\" (continuous/never-ending)\n        continuous: If True, task never completes (for monitors/watchers)\n    \"\"\"\n    classification = classify(message)\n    spawn_params = queue_spawn(classification, message, priority, mode, continuous)\n    \n    return {\n        \"classified\": True,\n        \"agent\": classification[\"agent\"],\n        \"model\": classification[\"model\"],\n        \"label\": spawn_params[\"label\"],\n        \"task\": message.strip()[:200],\n        \"priority\": priority,\n        \"confidence\": round(classification[\"confidence\"], 2),\n        \"queued\": True,\n        \"ready_to_spawn\": True,\n        \"mode\": mode,\n        \"continuous\": continuous,\n        \"sessions_spawn_params\": {\n            \"task\": message.strip(),\n            \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n            \"label\": spawn_params[\"label\"],\n            \"model\": classification[\"model\"],\n            \"timeoutSeconds\": 300 if not continuous else 0,  # 0 = no timeout for continuous\n            \"mode\": mode\n        }\n    }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":157033,"output":962,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772560709209}}
