{"type":"message","id":"d8767f43","parentId":"eb3cb6ba","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:00:26.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The thread option isn't available, but it still created a session. Let me check if the agent was spawned anyway and commit the changes.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3940458d214d4939acf3cd80","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if agent was spawned despite error\necho \"=== Active Subagents ===\" && subagents list 2>&1 | head -15\n\n# Commit all changes\ncd /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main && git add -A && git commit -m \"[feature] Task completion feedback + retry logic + continuous tasks\n\nIMPLEMENTED:\n1. Task Completion Feedback\n   - complete-task.py: Agents call when finished\n   - Updates spawn-pending.json with status\n   - Logs to task-completions.jsonl\n   - Status: ready→running→completed/failed\n\n2. Retry Logic (3x before dead letter)\n   - Tracks retry_count per task\n   - Auto-retries failed tasks up to 3 times\n   - Exhausted tasks → spawn-dead-letter.json\n   - Cleanup after 1 hour\n\n3. Continuous Task Support\n   - mode=\\\"session\\\" for never-ending tasks\n   - continuous=True flag in spawn queue\n   - timeoutSeconds=0 for no timeout\n   - continuous_tasks.py: Registry for heartbeat continuous tasks\n   - Example: ogedei_uptime_monitor (1min intervals)\n\nFILES:\n- chat_to_task.py: Added mode, continuous, retry_count params\n- spawn-consumer.sh: Retry logic, dead letter, cleanup\n- complete-task.py: NEW - completion handler\n- continuous_tasks.py: NEW - continuous task registry\n\nTESTED:\n- ✓ Task completion (mongke-1772559988 marked completed)\n- ✓ Continuous task classification (ogedei-1772560807)\n- ✓ Retry tracking in queue\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":163311,"output":436,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163747,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRe