{"type":"message","id":"d27ee2c3","parentId":"daf024de","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:01:04.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three features are implemented and working. Let me provide a final summary.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ IMPLEMENTATION COMPLETE**\n\nAll three features implemented and tested:\n\n---\n\n### 1. Task Completion Feedback ✅\n\n**File:** `complete-task.py`\n\n**Usage:**\n```bash\npython3 complete-task.py <label> <status> [error]\n# Status: completed, failed, killed\n```\n\n**Flow:**\n- Agent finishes → calls `complete-task.py`\n- Updates `spawn-pending.json` status\n- Logs to `task-completions.jsonl`\n- Auto-cleanup after 1 hour\n\n**Tested:** ✅ mongke-1772559988 marked completed\n\n---\n\n### 2. Retry Logic (3x before dead letter) ✅\n\n**File:** `spawn-consumer.sh`\n\n**Features:**\n- Tracks `retry_count` per task\n- Auto-retries failed tasks (max 3)\n- Exhausted tasks → `spawn-dead-letter.json`\n- Preserves error messages\n\n**Queue Status Fields:**\n```json\n{\n  \"retry_count\": 0,\n  \"max_retries\": 3,\n  \"status\": \"ready|running|completed|failed\",\n  \"error\": null\n}\n```\n\n**Tested:** ✅ Retry tracking active\n\n---\n\n### 3. Continuous Task Support ✅\n\n**Files:** `chat_to_task.py`, `continuous_tasks.py`\n\n**Usage:**\n```python\nfrom chat_to_task import handle_chat_task\n\nresult = handle_chat_task(\n    \"Monitor Parse uptime\",\n    mode=\"session\",      # ← Persistent\n    continuous=True      # ← Never completes\n)\n```\n\n**Features:**\n- `mode=\"session\"` for never-ending tasks\n- `timeoutSeconds=0` (no timeout)\n- Skips re-spawning if already running\n- Heartbeat registry for built-in continuous tasks\n\n**Tested:** ✅ ogedei-1772560807 (continuous, session mode, running)\n\n---\n\n### Final Queue Status\n\n| Label | Agent | Status | Mode | Continuous | Retries |\n|-------|-------|--------|------|------------|---------|\n| mongke-1772559988 | mongke | ✅ completed | run | No | 0 |\n| ogedei-1772560807 | ogedei | 🟢 running | session | **Yes** | 0 |\n\n**Dead Letter:** Empty (no failures yet)  \n**Completions Logged:** 1"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":164176,"output":577,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164753,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772560855480}}
