gistry now)\n   - Only processes ready non-continuous tasks\n   - Immediate cleanup of completed/failed\n\nBENEFITS:\n- Main queue stays clean (only active work)\n- Continuous tasks tracked separately with heartbeats\n- Completed tasks cleaned immediately (not 1 hour)\n- Better visibility into what's actually running\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":182268,"output":526,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":182794,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772561729739}}
