{"type":"message","id":"d841d7ce","parentId":"13b704ff","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:16:01.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me provide a comprehensive summary of what was implemented.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ IMPLEMENTATION COMPLETE**\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\n### 1. Immediate Cleanup of Completed Tasks ✅\n\n**Before:** Completed tasks waited 1 hour before cleanup  \n**After:** Removed immediately after completion\n\n**File:** `spawn-consumer.sh`\n```python\n# Old: Cleanup after 1 hour\ncutoff = datetime.now().timestamp() - 3600\nspawns = [s for s in spawns if ...]\n\n# New: Immediate cleanup\nspawns = [s for s in spawns if s.get('status') in ['ready', 'running']]\n```\n\n**Result:** Main queue only contains active work (ready + running)\n\n---\n\n### 2. Separate Continuous Task Registry ✅\n\n**File:** `continuous_registry.py` (NEW)\n\n**Commands:**\n```bash\n# Register a continuous task\npython3 continuous_registry.py register <label> <agent> <task>\n\n# List all continuous tasks\npython3 continuous_registry.py list\n\n# Unregister (stop) a task\npython3 continuous_registry.py unregister <label> [reason]\n\n# Check status\npython3 continuous_registry.py status <label>\n\n# Update heartbeat\npython3 continuous_registry.py heartbeat <label>\n```\n\n**Tracked Fields:**\n- `label`, `agent`, `task`\n- `session_key`\n- `started`, `stopped`\n- `last_heartbeat`, `heartbeats` (count)\n- `status` (running/stopped)\n- `stop_reason`\n\n**File:** `logs/continuous-tasks.json` (NEW)\n\n---\n\n### 3. Updated Integration\n\n**`chat_to_task.py`:**\n- Continuous tasks → `continuous_registry.py` (NOT main queue)\n- Regular tasks → `spawn-pending.json` (as before)\n\n**`spawn-consumer.sh`:**\n- Skips continuous tasks (handled separately)\n- Only processes ready non-continuous tasks\n- Immediate cleanup of completed/failed\n\n---\n\n### 4. Current State\n\n**Main Queue:** 2 tasks (both running)\n```\n- ogedei-1772560807: running\n- jochi-1772560963: running\n```\n\n**Continuous Registry:** 1 task (stopped - test)\n```\n- test-123 (ogedei) - stopped: manual\n```\n\n**Completions Log:** 2 entries\n```\n- mongke-1772559988: completed\n- test-123: completed (continuous)\n```\n\n---\n\n### Benefits\n\n| Benefit | Before | After |\n|---------|--------|-------|\n| **Queue Clarity** | Mixed (completed + running + ready) | Only active work |\n| **Continuous Tasks** | In main queue (confusing) | Separate registry |\n| **Cleanup Delay** | 1 hour | Immediate |\n| **Heartbeat Tracking** | None | Per-task heartbeat count |\n| **Visibility** | Hard to see what's running | Clear separation |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":184636,"output":687,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":185323,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772561754615}}
