{"type":"message","id":"db7c151e","parentId":"4c120f66","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:21:00.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All queries are working now. The task is complete. Let me provide a final summary.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ TASK COMPLETE**\n\n## Summary: Neo4j + JSON Queryable History for Task Tracking\n\n### What Was Implemented\n\n#### 1. Neo4j Task Tracker ✅\n**File:** `neo4j_task_tracker.py`\n\n**Schema:**\n```cypher\n(:Task {label, agent, status, created, completed, retry_count, ...})\n(:Agent {name})-[:EXECUTED]->(:Task)\n```\n\n**Methods:**\n| Method | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `create_task()` | Create task node |\n| `update_status()` | Update task status |\n| `get_tasks_by_agent()` | Query by agent |\n| `get_tasks_by_status()` | Query by status |\n| `get_hourly_summary()` | Summary for last N hours |\n| `get_completion_rate()` | Success/failure rates |\n| `get_continuous_tasks()` | Running continuous tasks |\n| `get_reflection_data()` | Data for hourly reflections |\n| `get_historical_trends()` | **NEW** Daily trends (7 days) |\n| `get_agent_workload()` | **NEW** Workload by agent |\n| `get_peak_hours()` | **NEW** Busiest hours |\n| `get_bottlenecks()` | **NEW** Tasks with most retries |\n\n---\n\n#### 2. JSON Queue + Completion Log ✅\n\n**Files:**\n- `spawn-pending.json` - Active tasks (ready + running)\n- `task-completions.jsonl` - Historical completion log\n\n**Immediate cleanup:** Completed tasks removed instantly (not 1 hour wait)\n\n---\n\n#### 3. Hourly Reflection Integration ✅\n\n**Files:** `reflection_data.py`, `hourly_reflection.sh`\n\n**Metrics in Reflections:**\n```markdown\n## 📊 Task Metrics (Neo4j)\n\n**Last Hour:**\n- Tasks: 5 total, 4 completed, 1 failed\n- Success Rate: 80.0%\n- Retries: 2\n- Avg Duration: 45s\n- Continuous: 1 running\n\n### Recent Tasks\n- [completed] mongke-123: Research X...\n- [running] ogedei-456: Monitor uptime...\n\n### Historical Trends (7 days)\n- Daily trends: 7 days of data\n- Workload by agent: 6 agents\n- Peak hours: Top 5 busiest\n- Bottlenecks: Tasks with retries\n```\n\n**Usage:**\n```bash\n# Agent reflection\npython3 reflection_data.py --agent temujin --hours 1\n\n# Kurultai summary\npython3 reflection_data.py --kurultai --hours 1\n\n# With historical trends\npython3 reflection_data.py --kurultai --hours 1 --trends\n```\n\n---\n\n### Tested & Verified ✅\n\n| Test | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| Task creation → Neo4j | ✅ Working |\n| Task completion → Neo4j | ✅ Working |\n| Reflection data query | ✅ Working |\n| Historical trends | ✅ Working |\n| Agent workload | ✅ Working |\n| Peak hours | ✅ Working |\n| Bottlenecks | ✅ Working |\n| Division by zero fix | ✅ Fixed |\n| Hourly reflection integration | ✅ Integrated |\n\n---\n\n**The task is 100% complete.** All features implemented, tested, and integrated into hourly Kurultai reflections."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":198026,"output":776,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":198802,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772562053412}}
