{"type":"message","id":"d30264ce","parentId":"f15f3f96","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:22:22.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to integrate the meta-reflection into the hourly reflection script so it runs automatically for all agents every hour.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 4. Integrate into Hourly Reflection Script\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_21cc04820a6a44b6a53be0fd","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/hourly_reflection.sh","oldText":"## 📊 Task Metrics (Neo4j)\n\n**Last Hour:**\n\n```bash\n$(python3 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/reflection_data.py --agent $AGENT --hours 1 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\ntry:\n    d=json.load(sys.stdin)\n    t=d.get('tasks',{})\n    print(f\\\"\\\"\\\"- Tasks: {t.get('total',0)} total, {t.get('completed',0)} completed, {t.get('failed',0)} failed\n- Success Rate: {t.get('success_rate','N/A')}\n- Retries: {t.get('retries',0)}\n- Avg Duration: {t.get('avg_duration_seconds','N/A')}s\n- Continuous: {d.get('continuous_tasks',0)} running\\\"\\\"\\\")\nexcept:\n    print('- Neo4j metrics unavailable')\n\" 2>/dev/null)\n```","newText":"## 📊 Task Metrics (Neo4j)\n\n**Last Hour:**\n\n```bash\n$(python3 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/reflection_data.py --agent $AGENT --hours 1 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\ntry:\n    d=json.load(sys.stdin)\n    t=d.get('tasks',{})\n    print(f\\\"\\\"\\\"- Tasks: {t.get('total',0)} total, {t.get('completed',0)} completed, {t.get('failed',0)} failed\n- Success Rate: {t.get('success_rate','N/A')}\n- Retries: {t.get('retries',0)}\n- Avg Duration: {t.get('avg_duration_seconds','N/A')}s\n- Continuous: {d.get('continuous_tasks',0)} running\\\"\\\"\\\")\nexcept:\n    print('- Neo4j metrics unavailable')\n\" 2>/dev/null)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🤔 Meta-Reflection: System Evaluation\n\n**As $AGENT, critically evaluate the task/spawning system:**\n\n```bash\n$(python3 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/meta_reflection.py --agent $AGENT --hours 1 2>/dev/null | tail -n +10 | head -50)\n```\n\n### Your Feedback to Kublai\n\n**Submit system improvement ideas:**\n\n1. **Bottlenecks observed:** [What's slow or broken?]\n2. **Improvement ideas:** [What would make it better?]\n3. **Agent coordination:** [Any collaboration opportunities?]\n4. **Priority:** [ ] CRITICAL  [ ] HIGH  [ ] MEDIUM  [ ] LOW\n\n**Submit via:**\n```bash\npython3 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/meta_reflection.py \\\n  --agent $AGENT \\\n  --submit\n```\n\n---"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":204242,"output":749,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":204991,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772562135031}}
