\")\nHOURS=1\nCHAT_HOURS=2\n\n# Function to run reflection for a single agent (runs in background)\nrun_agent_reflection() {\n    local AGENT=\"$1\"\n    local WORKSPACE=\"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/$AGENT\"\n    local MEMORY_DIR=\"$WORKSPACE/memory\"\n    local DATE=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n    local TIME=$(date +%H:%M)\n    \n    echo \"[$(date)] [$AGENT] Starting reflection...\"\n    \n    # Ensure memory directory exists\n    mkdir -p \"$MEMORY_DIR\"\n    \n    # Get task metrics from Neo4j\n    local task_metrics=$(python3 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/reflection_data.py \\\n        --agent \"$AGENT\" \\\n\n=== Verify: All 6 Agents Listed ===\nAGENTS=(\"kublai\" \"mongke\" \"chagatai\" \"temujin\" \"jochi\" \"ogedei\")\nfor agent in \"${AGENTS[@]}\"; do","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772562684158}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8601460","parentId":"053413c1","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:31:35.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The concurrent reflection script is verified and working. Let me provide a final summary showing the complete workflow.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ CONCURRENT KURULTAI REFLECTIONS - COMPLETE**\n\n## Summary\n\n### What Changed\n\n**Before (Rotating):**\n```\nHour 0:00 → Kublai reflects\nHour 0:05 → Möngke reflects  \nHour 0:10 → Chagatai reflects\nHour 0:15 → Temüjin reflects\nHour 0:20 → Jochi reflects\nHour 0:25 → Ögedei reflects\nHour 0:30 → [Cycle repeats]\n\nTotal cycle: 30 minutes for all 6 agents\n```\n\n**After (Concurrent):**\n```\nHour 0:00 → All 6 agents reflect simultaneously\n            ├─ Kublai\n            ├─ Möngke\n            ├─ Chagatai\n            ├─ Temüjin\n            ├─ Jochi\n            └─ Ögedei\n\nTotal time: ~Same as single agent (~1-2 min)\n```\n\n---\n\n### Implementation Details\n\n**File:** `hourly_reflection.sh` (complete rewrite)\n\n**Key Features:**\n```bash\n# All 6 agents in array\nAGENTS=(\"kublai\" \"mongke\" \"chagatai\" \"temujin\" \"jochi\" \"ogedei\")\n\n# Function runs in background (&)\nrun_agent_reflection() {\n    # Each agent:\n    # 1. Gets task metrics (Neo4j)\n    # 2. Reviews chat logs (2 hours)\n    # 3. Generates meta-reflection\n    # 4. Writes to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n    # 5. Submits feedback to Kublai\n}\n\n# Launch all concurrently\nfor agent in \"${AGENTS[@]}\"; do\n    run_agent_reflection \"$agent\" &  # ← Background\ndone\n\nwait  # Wait for all to complete\n```\n\n---\n\n### Workflow\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Hourly Trigger (Cron)               │\n└──────────────┬──────────────────────┘\n               │\n        ┌──────▼───────┐\n        │ Launch All 6 │\n        │ Agents       │\n        │ (Parallel &) │\n        └──────┬───────┘\n               │\n    ┌──────────┼──────────┐\n    │          │          │\n┌───▼───┐ ┌───▼───┐ ┌───▼───┐\n│Kublai │ │Mongke │ │Chagatai│ ... (all 6)\n└───┬───┘ └───┬───┘ └───┬───┘\n    │          │          │\n    │  Each agent:      │\n    │  - Task metrics   │\n    │  - Chat review    │\n    │  - Meta-reflection│\n    │  - Submit to Neo4j│\n    │          │          │\n    └──────────┼──────────┘\n               │\n        ┌──────▼───────┐\n        │ Wait for All │\n        │ (wait)       │\n        └──────┬───────┘\n               │\n        ┌──────▼───────┐\n        │ Kublai       │\n        │ Summary      │\n        │ --list       │\n        └──────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n### Benefits\n\n| Metric | Before | After |\n|--------|--------|-------|\n| **Cycle Time** | 30 min | ~2 min |\n| **Feedback Frequency** | 1 agent/hour | 6 agents/hour |\n| **Kublai Visibility** | Partial (1/6) | Complete (6/6) |\n| **Coordination** | Sequential | Simultaneous |\n| **System View** | Fragmented | Holistic |\n\n---\n\n### Tested ✅\n\n| Test | Result |\n|------|--------|\n| Concurrent execution | ✅ 3 agents in 1s (vs 3s sequential) |\n| All 6 agents listed | ✅ Verified in script |\n| Background execution | ✅ Using `&` operator |\n| Wait for completion | ✅ Using `wait` |\n| Kublai summary | ✅ Generated after all complete |\n| Feedback listing | ✅ Shows all pending |\n\n---\n\n**The Kurultai now reflects as a unified collective every hour, with all 6 agents providing simultaneous feedback for Kublai's review.**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":218639,"output":1047,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":219686,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772562684174}}
