{"type":"message","id":"f0ea6061","parentId":"d5ab899f","timestamp":"2026-03-03T19:06:11.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Silent mode is now working - no output when there's no activity. Let me provide a summary of what was implemented.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**✅ SILENT MODE COMPLETE**\n\n## Summary\n\n### What Changed\n\n**File:** `spawn-consumer.sh`\n\n**New Behavior:**\n- **Silent mode (default):** No output when 0 spawns, 0 retries\n- **Verbose mode:** Reports every cycle (for debugging)\n\n**Configuration:**\n```bash\n# Silent (default) - only report meaningful activity\nREPORT_ONLY_ON_ACTIVITY=true\n\n# Verbose - report all cycles\nREPORT_ONLY_ON_ACTIVITY=false\n```\n\n---\n\n### Before vs After\n\n| Before | After |\n|--------|-------|\n| Every 2-min cycle reported | Only reports on activity |\n| \"~15 chat messages/hour\" (empty cycles) | \"~0-2 messages/hour\" (actual spawns) |\n| Hard to find important events | Important events stand out |\n| Chat spam from no-op cycles | Clean chat history |\n\n---\n\n### When Chat Messages Appear\n\n**Now you'll only see messages when:**\n\n1. **Agents spawned:**\n   ```\n   === Spawn Consumer Cycle ===\n   SPAWN: temujin (qwen3.5-plus, run) - temujin-1772561234\n   PROCESSED: 1 spawns, 0 retries, 5 remaining\n   === Cycle Complete ===\n   ```\n\n2. **Retries occurred:**\n   ```\n   === Spawn Consumer Cycle ===\n   RETRY: mongke-1772560000 (attempt 2/3)\n   PROCESSED: 0 spawns, 1 retries, 3 remaining\n   === Cycle Complete ===\n   ```\n\n3. **Tasks failed (dead letter):**\n   ```\n   === Spawn Consumer Cycle ===\n   FAILED: jochi-1772560000 (max retries exceeded)\n   === Cycle Complete ===\n   ```\n\n**Empty cycles:** Completely silent (no output)\n\n---\n\n### Tested ✅\n\n| Test | Result |\n|------|--------|\n| Silent mode (no activity) | ✅ No output |\n| Verbose mode | ✅ Shows all cycles |\n| Spawn detection | ✅ Reports when agents spawned |\n| Retry detection | ✅ Reports on retries |\n\n---\n\n**Chat will now only show novel agent executions, not empty cycle summaries.**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":227484,"output":552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":228036,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772564764287}}
