{"type":"message","id":"d719745f","parentId":"e9f8173a","timestamp":"2026-03-03T19:06:12.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**✅ SILENT MODE COMPLETE**\n\n## Summary\n\n### What Changed\n\n**File:** `spawn-consumer.sh`\n\n**New Behavior:**\n- **Silent mode (default):** No output when 0 spawns, 0 retries\n- **Verbose mode:** Reports every cycle (for debugging)\n\n**Configuration:**\n```bash\n# Silent (default) - only report meaningful activity\nREPORT_ONLY_ON_ACTIVITY=true\n\n# Verbose - report all cycles\nREPORT_ONLY_ON_ACTIVITY=false\n```\n\n---\n\n### Before vs After\n\n| Before | After |\n|--------|-------|\n| Every 2-min cycle reported | Only reports on activity |\n| \"~15 chat messages/hour\" (empty cycles) | \"~0-2 messages/hour\" (actual spawns) |\n| Hard to find important events | Important events stand out |\n| Chat spam from no-op cycles | Clean chat history |\n\n---\n\n### When Chat Messages Appear\n\n**Now you'll only see messages when:**\n\n1. **Agents spawned:**\n   ```\n   === Spawn Consumer Cycle ===\n   SPAWN: temujin (qwen3.5-plus, run) - temujin-1772561234\n   PROCESSED: 1 spawns, 0 retries, 5 remaining\n   === Cycle Complete ===\n   ```\n\n2. **Retries occurred:**\n   ```\n   === Spawn Consumer Cycle ===\n   RETRY: mongke-1772560000 (attempt 2/3)\n   PROCESSED: 0 spawns, 1 retries, 3 remaining\n   === Cycle Complete ===\n   ```\n\n3. **Tasks failed (dead letter):**\n   ```\n   === Spawn Consumer Cycle ===\n   FAILED: jochi-1772560000 (max retries exceeded)\n   === Cycle Complete ===\n   ```\n\n**Empty cycles:** Completely silent (no output)\n\n---\n\n### Tested ✅\n\n| Test | Result |\n|------|--------|\n| Silent mode (no activity) | ✅ No output |\n| Verbose mode | ✅ Shows all cycles |\n| Spawn detection | ✅ Reports when agents spawned |\n| Retry detection | ✅ Reports on retries |\n\n---\n\n**Chat will now only show novel agent executions, not empty cycle summaries.**"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772564772839}}
{"type":"message","id":"829389c0","parentId":"d719745f","timestamp":"2026-03-03T19:06:26.972Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Spawn Consumer executed successfully at 14:06:04.\n\n**Currently Running Agents:**\n\n1. **ogedei** \n   - Model: qwen3.5-plus\n   - Mode: session (continuous)\n   - Task: Monitor Parse uptime every minute\n   - Status: running since 13:00:13\n   - Priority: high\n\n2. **jochi**\n   - Model: MiniMax-M2.5\n   - Mode: run\n   - Task: Test Neo4j tracking\n   - Status: running since 13:04:15\n   - Priority: normal\n\n**Queue Status:** 0 pending spawns, 2 active agents\n\nNo new agents were spawned in this cycle — both existing spawns are already running. The consumer will continue monitoring the queue every 2 minutes for new spawn requests."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772564786972}}
{"type":"message","id":"75104192","parentId":"829389c0","timestamp":"2026-03-03T19:06:55.151Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"0b75897b-e4d1-40f9-b87d-0730b87ca2b9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"sender\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 14:06 EST] explain what happens each heartbeat"}],"timestamp":1772564815145}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d60c10a","parentId":"75104192","timestamp":"2026-03-03T19:07:22.133Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to explain what happens during each heartbeat cycle in the Kurultai system. Let me trace through the complete heartbeat flow based on what we've implemented.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Heartbeat System Explained\n\n### System Overview\n\nThere are **two separate heartbeat systems** running:\n\n---\n\n## 1. Kurultai Heartbeat Daemon (Every 5 Minutes)\n\n**Location:** `/Users/kublai/kurultai/kublai-repo/tools/kurultai/heartbeat_master.py`\n\n**What It Does:**\n- Runs as a standalone Python daemon (outside OpenClaw)\n- Executes registered tasks for all 6 agents\n- Writes to spawn queue when tasks are found\n\n**Schedule (24 tasks total):**\n\n| Agent | Task | Frequency | What It Does |\n|-------|------|-----------|--------------|\n| **kublai** | status_synthesis | 5 min | Synthesizes system status |\n| **kublai** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls kublai/tasks/ for work |\n| **kublai** | kublai_review | 60 min | Reviews pending proposals |\n| **temujin** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls temujin/tasks/ for code work |\n| **temujin** | code_review | 60 min | Reviews Parse code for errors |\n| **mongke** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls mongke/tasks/ for research |\n| **mongke** | quick_research | 60 min | Researches trending topics |\n| **mongke** | knowledge_gap | 1440 min | Analyzes knowledge gaps (daily) |\n| **mongke** | ordo_sacer | 1440 min | Esoteric research (daily) |\n| **mongke** | ecosystem | 10080 min | Ecosystem intel (weekly) |\n| **chagatai** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls chagatai/tasks/ for writing |\n| **chagatai** | content_generation | 60 min | Generates content when idle |\n| **chagatai** | reflection_consolidation | 30 min | Consolidates reflections |\n| **jochi** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls jochi/tasks/ for testing |\n| **jochi** | memory_curation_rapid | 5 min | Enforces token budgets |\n| **jochi** | smoke_tests | 15 min | Runs quick smoke tests |\n| **jochi** | full_tests | 60 min | Full test suite |\n| **jochi** | deep_curation | 360 min | Deep memory cleanup (6hr) |\n| **ogedei** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls ogedei/tasks/ for ops |\n| **ogedei** | health_check | 5 min | Checks Neo4j, gateway, disk |\n| **ogedei** | file_consistency | 15 min | Verifies file consistency |\n| **system** | notion_sync | 60 min | Notion↔Neo4j sync |\n| **system** | agent_reflection | 60 min | One agent reflects (rotating) |\n| **system** | validate_improvements | 60 min | Validates 24h improvements |\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nHeartbeat Daemon (5 min)\n        ↓\nChecks each agent's task directory\n        ↓\nFinds tasks? → Writes to spawn-pending.json\n        ↓\nNo tasks? → Does nothing (silent)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. OpenClaw Cron Jobs (Every 1-60 Minutes)\n\n**Location:** OpenClaw Gateway cron configuration\n\n### A. Spawn Consumer (Every 2 Minutes)\n\n**Script:** `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/spawn-consumer.sh`\n\n**What It Does:**\n1. Reads `spawn-pending.json`\n2. Finds tasks with `status: \"ready\"`\n3. Outputs spawn commands for execution\n4. Updates status to `running`\n5. **Silent mode:** Only reports if activity detected\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nspawn-pending.json (ready tasks)\n        ↓\nspawn-consumer.sh (2 min)\n        ↓\nOutputs: SPAWN_CMD|agent|model|label|task\n        ↓\nsessions_spawn executes\n        ↓\nStatus: ready → running\n```\n\n### B. Hourly Reflection (Every Hour)\n\n**Script:** `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/hourly_reflection.sh`\n\n**What It Does:**\n1. **All 6 agents run concurrently** (not rotating anymore)\n2. Each agent:\n   - Gets task metrics from Neo4j (last 1 hour)\n   - Reviews chat logs (last 2 hours)\n   - Reads ARCHITECTURE.md context\n   - Generates meta-reflection\n   - Writes to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n   - Submits feedback to Neo4j (AgentFeedback node)\n3. Kublai summary generated\n4. Pending feedback listed for review\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nHourly Trigger\n        ↓\nAll 6 agents (parallel)\n        ↓\nEach agent:\n  - Task metrics (Neo4j)\n  - Chat log review (2hr)\n  - Meta-reflection\n  - Submit to Kublai\n        ↓\nKublai reviews feedback\n        ↓\nApproves → Creates tasks\n        ↓\nTasks → spawn-pending.json\n```\n\n### C. Task Consumer (Every 15 Minutes)\n\n**Script:** `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/task-consumer.sh`\n\n**What It Does:**\n1. Polls each agent's task directory\n2. Finds pending tasks (high/normal/low-*.md)\n3. Marks as executing\n4. Logs execution\n\n---\n\n## Complete Heartbeat Flow (Timeline)\n\n```\nTime    Event\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n:00     Hourly Reflection (all 6 agents concurrent)\n        ├─ Task metrics (Neo4j)\n        ├─ Chat log review (2hr)\n        ├─ Meta-reflection\n        └─ Submit feedback to Kublai\n        \n:02     Spawn Consumer (silent if no activity)\n:04     Spawn Consumer (silent if no activity)\n:05     Kurultai Heartbeat (24 tasks across 6 agents)\n        ├─ task_pickup for all agents\n        ├─ health_check (ogedei)\n        └─ memory_curation (jochi)\n:06     Spawn Consumer\n:08     Spawn Consumer\n:10     Kurultai Heartbeat\n:10     Spawn Consumer\n:12     Spawn Consumer\n:15     Kurultai Heartbeat\n        ├─ smoke_tests (jochi)\n        └─ file_consistency (ogedei)\n:15     Task Consumer (15 min)\n:14     Spawn Consumer\n...     (continues)\n:60     [Cycle repeats]\n```\n\n---\n\n## Task Lifecycle\n\n```\n1. Task Created\n   ├─ Chat message → chat_to_task.py → spawn-pending.json\n   ├─ Heartbeat task_pickup → spawn-pending.json\n   └─ Kublai approval → spawn-pending.json\n\n2. Task Queued\n   └─ Status: \"ready\"\n\n3. Spawn Consumer (2 min)\n   ├─ Finds ready tasks\n   ├─ Outputs SPAWN_CMD\n   └─ Status: \"ready\" → \"running\"\n\n4. Agent Executes\n   ├─ sessions_spawn creates subagent\n   ├─ Subagent completes task\n   └─ complete-task.py marks \"completed\"\n\n5. Cleanup\n   └─ Completed tasks removed from queue (immediate)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Continuous Tasks\n\nSome tasks never complete (monitors, watchers):\n\n| Task | Agent | Frequency | Status |\n|------|-------|-----------|--------|\n| Parse uptime monitor | ogedei | Continuous | running |\n\n**Handling:**\n- Registered in `continuous-tasks.json` (separate from main queue)\n- Heartbeat checks if already running (skips if yes)\n- Can be stopped via `subagents action=kill`\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| System | Frequency | Purpose | Output |\n|--------|-----------|---------|--------|\n| **Kurultai Heartbeat** | 5 min | Execute agent tasks | spawn-pending.json |\n| **Spawn Consumer** | 2 min | Execute queued spawns | sessions_spawn |\n| **Hourly Reflection** | 60 min | Agent meta-reflection | AgentFeedback (Neo4j) |\n| **Task Consumer** | 15 min | Poll task directories | Logs execution |\n\n**Chat Messages:** Only when spawn consumer finds actual work (silent on empty cycles)"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":228428,"output":2000,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":230428,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772564815148}}
