ei** | task_pickup | 5 min | Polls ogedei/tasks/ for ops |\n| **ogedei** | health_check | 5 min | Checks Neo4j, gateway, disk |\n| **ogedei** | file_consistency | 15 min | Verifies file consistency |\n| **system** | notion_sync | 60 min | Notion↔Neo4j sync |\n| **system** | agent_reflection | 60 min | One agent reflects (rotating) |\n| **system** | validate_improvements | 60 min | Validates 24h improvements |\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nHeartbeat Daemon (5 min)\n        ↓\nChecks each agent's task directory\n        ↓\nFinds tasks? → Writes to spawn-pending.json\n        ↓\nNo tasks? → Does nothing (silent)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. OpenClaw Cron Jobs (Every 1-60 Minutes)\n\n**Location:** OpenClaw Gateway cron configuration\n\n### A. Spawn Consumer (Every 2 Minutes)\n\n**Script:** `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/spawn-consumer.sh`\n\n**What It Does:**\n1. Reads `spawn-pending.json`\n2. Finds tasks with `status: \"ready\"`\n3. Outputs spawn commands for execution\n4. Updates status to `running`\n5. **Silent mode:** Only reports if activity detected\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nspawn-pending.json (ready tasks)\n        ↓\nspawn-consumer.sh (2 min)\n        ↓\nOutputs: SPAWN_CMD|agent|model|label|task\n        ↓\nsessions_spawn executes\n        ↓\nStatus: ready → running\n```\n\n### B. Hourly Reflection (Every Hour)\n\n**Script:** `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/hourly_reflection.sh`\n\n**What It Does:**\n1. **All 6 agents run concurrently** (not rotating anymore)\n2. Each agent:\n   - Gets task metrics from Neo4j (last 1 hour)\n   - Reviews chat logs (last 2 hours)\n   - Reads ARCHITECTURE.md context\n   - Generates meta-reflection\n   - Writes to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n   - Submits feedback to Neo4j (AgentFeedback node)\n3. Kublai summary generated\n4. Pending feedback listed for review\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nHourly Trigger\n        ↓\nAll 6 agents (parallel)\n        ↓\nEach agent:\n  - Task metrics (Neo4j)\n  - Chat log review (2hr)\n  - Meta-reflection\n  - Submit