atus |\n|------|-------|-----------|--------|\n| Parse uptime monitor | ogedei | Continuous | running |\n\n**Handling:**\n- Registered in `continuous-tasks.json` (separate from main queue)\n- Heartbeat checks if already running (skips if yes)\n- Can be stopped via `subagents action=kill`\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| System | Frequency | Purpose | Output |\n|--------|-----------|---------|--------|\n| **Kurultai Heartbeat** | 5 min | Execute agent tasks | spawn-pending.json |\n| **Spawn Consumer** | 2 min | Execute queued spawns | sessions_spawn |\n| **Hourly Reflection** | 60 min | Agent meta-reflection | AgentFeedback (Neo4j) |\n| **Task Consumer** | 15 min | Poll task directories | Logs execution |\n\n**Chat Messages:** Only when spawn consumer finds actual work (silent on empty cycles)"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772564844792}}
