{"type":"message","id":"35a2fb1b","parentId":"81615eba","timestamp":"2026-03-03T19:48:32.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Spawn Consumer Report**\n\n**Execution Time:** 2:48 PM EST, March 3, 2026\n\n**Spawn Queue Status:** Empty (no pending spawns)\n\n**Agents Spawned This Cycle:** None\n\n**Recent Activity (Last 60 Minutes):**\n- 1 subagent completed: `jochi-1772560963`\n  - Task: Test Neo4j tracking\n  - Model: qwen3.5-plus\n  - Runtime: 1 minute\n  - Status: Done\n\n**Active Subagents:** 0\n\n**Consumer Health:** Running normally (cycling every 2 minutes via cron)\n\nThe spawn consumer executed successfully but found no pending spawn requests in the queue. The system is operational and ready to process new spawn requests when they arrive."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772567312023}}
