{"type":"message","id":"abb53d6b","parentId":"81a92cf0","timestamp":"2026-03-03T23:07:13.569Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to follow HEARTBEAT.md. Let me check what it says and run the heartbeat checklist.\n\nLooking at the earlier conversation, HEARTBEAT.md was read and it contains:\n- Quick Check every 30m (Gateway, Sessions, Parse, LLM Survivor, Agent Health, Self-Direction)\n- Deep Reflection every 6 hours\n- If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK\n\nLet me run through the quick check items:\n1. Gateway status\n2. Sessions activity\n3. Parse health\n4. LLM Survivor health\n5. Agent health (any CRITICAL escalations?)\n6. Subagents stuck?\n7. Self-direction review\n\nLet me run these checks quickly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dfa8392d29604782aea7c0af","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# HEARTBEAT Quick Check\necho \"=== HEARTBEAT Quick Check ===\" \n\n# 1. Gateway status\necho \"1. Gateway:\"\nopenclaw gateway status 2>&1 | grep -E \"Runtime:|running\" | head -1\n\n# 2. Parse health\necho \"2. Parse:\"\ncurl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\\n\" https://parsethe.media/ 2>/dev/null\n\n# 3. LLM Survivor\necho \"3. LLM Survivor:\"\ncurl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\\n\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/ 2>/dev/null\n\n# 4. Agent health (Neo4j)\necho \"4. Agents:\"\npython3 -c \"\nfrom neo4j import GraphDatabase\ndriver = GraphDatabase.driver('bolt://localhost:7687', auth=('neo4j', 'myStrongPassword123'))\nwith driver.session() as session:\n    result = session.run('MATCH (a:AgentState) RETURN count(a) AS count, sum(CASE WHEN a.status=\\\"running\\\" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS running')\n    r = result.single()\n    print(f'{r[\\\"running\\\"]}/{r[\\\"count\\\"]} agents running')\ndriver.close()\n\" 2>&1 | head -1\n\n# 5. Subagents\necho \"5. Subagents:\"\npython3 -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw')\ntry:\n    from openclaw.tools import subagents\n    r = subagents(action='list')\n    print(f'{r.get(\\\"total\\\", 0)} active, {len(r.get(\\\"recent\\\", []))} recent')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'Check failed: {e}')\n\" 2>&1 | head -1\n\n# 6. Spawn consumer\necho \"6. Spawn Consumer:\"\nlaunchctl list | grep -c spawn-consumer && echo \"Running\" || echo \"Not running\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":354946,"output":802,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":355748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772579185762}}
