{"type":"message","id":"cdc8db4e","parentId":"b85558d5","timestamp":"2026-03-03T23:26:34.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue - there's a cron job pointing to `/Users/kublai/scripts/heartbeat_monitor.sh` but the actual script is at `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh`. The paths don't match.\n\nLet me create a task for Ogedei (Operations agent) to fix this cron configuration error.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3f55aafebc354742a2f7a7a3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nagent: ogedei\npriority: high\ncreated: 2026-03-03T18:25:00\nsource: kublai_direct\n---\n\n# Task: Fix heartbeat-watchdog Cron Configuration Error\n\n## Issue Identified\n\nThe heartbeat-watchdog cron job has incorrect paths:\n\n**Current (WRONG):**\n```bash\n*/15 * * * * /Users/kublai/scripts/heartbeat_monitor.sh >> /tmp/heartbeat_monitor.log 2>&1\n```\n\n**Problems:**\n1. Script path `/Users/kublai/scripts/heartbeat_monitor.sh` doesn't exist\n2. Actual script is at `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh`\n3. Log file `/tmp/heartbeat_monitor.log` should be in proper logs directory\n\n## Fix Required\n\n### 1. Update Crontab\n\nEdit crontab to use correct path:\n```bash\ncrontab -e\n\n# Replace this line:\n*/15 * * * * /Users/kublai/scripts/heartbeat_monitor.sh >> /tmp/heartbeat_monitor.log 2>&1\n\n# With:\n*/5 * * * * /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh >> /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/heartbeat-watchdog.log 2>&1\n```\n\n### 2. Verify Script is Executable\n\n```bash\nchmod +x /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh\nls -la /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh\n```\n\n### 3. Test Script Manually\n\n```bash\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh\necho \"Exit code: $?\"\n```\n\n### 4. Verify Cron is Working\n\nAfter updating crontab:\n```bash\n# List cron jobs\ncrontab -l | grep heartbeat\n\n# Check log file after 5 minutes\ntail /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/heartbeat-watchdog.log\n```\n\n## Alternative: Use LaunchAgent Instead\n\nIf cron is unreliable on macOS, create a LaunchAgent:\n\n```bash\ncat > /Users/kublai/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.heartbeat-watchdog.plist << 'EOF'\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN\" \"http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">\n<plist version=\"1.0\">\n<dict>\n    <key>Label</key>\n    <string>ai.openclaw.heartbeat-watchdog</string>\n    \n    <key>ProgramArguments</key>\n    <array>\n        <string>/bin/bash</string>\n        <string>/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh</string>\n    </array>\n    \n    <key>StartInterval</key>\n    <integer>300</integer>\n    \n    <key>StandardOutPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/heartbeat-watchdog.log</string>\n    \n    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>\n    <string>/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/heartbeat-watchdog.err</string>\n    \n    <key>RunAtLoad</key>\n    <true/>\n</dict>\n</plist>\nEOF\n\nlaunchctl load /Users/kublai/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.heartbeat-watchdog.plist\n```\n\n## Deliverables\n\n1. ✅ Crontab updated with correct path\n2. ✅ Script verified executable\n3. ✅ Script tested manually (exit code 0)\n4. ✅ Cron verified working OR LaunchAgent created and loaded\n5. ✅ Log file being written\n\n---\n\nExecute this task and report completion.\n","path":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/ogedei/tasks/high-1772580300.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":362607,"output":1091,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":363698,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772580373568}}
