{"type":"message","id":"723616ee","parentId":"450c087d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T23:48:19.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to fix the heartbeat-watchdog cron. Earlier I found that the cron was pointing to the wrong path. Let me check the current state and fix it properly.\n\nFrom earlier investigation:\n- Current (WRONG) cron: `*/15 * * * * /Users/kublai/scripts/heartbeat_monitor.sh >> /tmp/heartbeat_monitor.log 2>&1`\n- Actual script location: `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh`\n\nI need to:\n1. Check current crontab\n2. Fix the heartbeat-watchdog cron path\n3. Verify the script is executable\n4. Test the script\n5. Verify cron is working\n\nLet me do this now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bb921351e9ae4d20894fe12f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Fix heartbeat-watchdog cron\necho \"=== Fixing heartbeat-watchdog Cron ===\" \n\n# 1. Check current crontab\necho \"1. Current crontab:\"\ncrontab -l 2>&1 | grep -E \"heartbeat|spawn|task\" | head -10\n\n# 2. Fix the heartbeat-watchdog path\necho \"\" && echo \"2. Fixing heartbeat-watchdog cron path...\"\n\n# Get current crontab, remove old heartbeat entries\ncrontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -v -E \"heartbeat_monitor|heartbeat-watchdog\" > /tmp/crontab-fixed.txt\n\n# Add correct heartbeat-watchdog cron (every 5 minutes)\ncat >> /tmp/crontab-fixed.txt << 'EOF'\n# Heartbeat watchdog - monitors heartbeat daemon every 5 min\n*/5 * * * * /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh >> /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/heartbeat-watchdog.log 2>&1\nEOF\n\n# Install fixed crontab\ncrontab /tmp/crontab-fixed.txt 2>&1 && echo \"  ✓ Crontab updated\" || echo \"  ⚠ Crontab update failed\"\n\n# 3. Verify script is executable\necho \"\" && echo \"3. Verifying script permissions:\"\nchmod +x /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh\nls -la /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh\n\n# 4. Test script manually\necho \"\" && echo \"4. Testing heartbeat-watchdog.sh manually:\"\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh 2>&1 | head -10\necho \"  Exit code: $?\"\n\n# 5. Verify updated crontab\necho \"\" && echo \"5. Updated crontab (heartbeat/spawn/task entries):\"\ncrontab -l 2>&1 | grep -E \"heartbeat|spawn|task\" | head -10\n\n# 6. Check LaunchAgent for heartbeat daemon\necho \"\" && echo \"6. Heartbeat daemon LaunchAgent:\"\nlaunchctl list | grep -i heartbeat | head -3"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":380402,"output":832,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":381234,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772581682703}}
