{"type":"message","id":"4ced2360","parentId":"0cf5d71c","timestamp":"2026-03-03T23:59:33.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reporting that the heartbeat-watchdog cron is in an error state. Let me check what's wrong with it and fix it.\n\nI need to:\n1. Check the current status of the heartbeat-watchdog\n2. Check the cron job\n3. Check the LaunchAgent\n4. Fix whatever is broken","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ef9176d7f212461cac05bcbb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Diagnose heartbeat-watchdog error\necho \"=== Diagnosing heartbeat-watchdog Error ===\" \n\n# 1. Check LaunchAgent status\necho \"1. LaunchAgent Status:\"\nlaunchctl list | grep -i heartbeat 2>&1 || echo \"  No heartbeat LaunchAgent found\"\n\n# 2. Check LaunchAgent plist exists\necho \"\" && echo \"2. LaunchAgent plist:\"\nls -la /Users/kublai/Library/LaunchAgents/*heartbeat* 2>/dev/null || echo \"  File not found\"\n\n# 3. Check cron job\necho \"\" && echo \"3. Cron job:\"\ncrontab -l 2>&1 | grep heartbeat || echo \"  No heartbeat cron found\"\n\n# 4. Check log files\necho \"\" && echo \"4. Log files:\"\nls -la /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/*heartbeat* 2>/dev/null | tail -5 || echo \"  No log files\"\n\n# 5. Check script exists and is executable\necho \"\" && echo \"5. Script status:\"\nls -la /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh 2>/dev/null || echo \"  Script not found\"\n\n# 6. Test script manually\necho \"\" && echo \"6. Testing script manually:\"\n/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/heartbeat-watchdog.sh 2>&1 | head -10\necho \"Exit code: $?\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":389534,"output":480,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":390014,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772582360435}}
