{"type":"message","id":"7292bf96","parentId":"8ea01f17","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:17:36.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to test Mongke (the researcher agent) with a research task about creating a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections. This will verify that the direct execution flow works for Mongke as well, not just Temujin.\n\nLet me use direct-execute.py to send this task to Mongke and verify it completes successfully.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c649d7288c314e5e965b06be","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test Mongke Research Task\necho \"=== Testing Mongke: Prompt Injection Sandbox Research ===\" \necho \"\"\necho \"Task: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Execute task directly with Mongke\necho \"1. Sending research task to Mongke via direct-execute.py...\"\npython3 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/direct-execute.py \\\n    --task \"Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections. Include: 1) existing tools/libraries, 2) isolation strategies, 3) safety measures, 4) implementation approach\" \\\n    --priority high 2>&1\n\n# Wait for execution\nsleep 3\n\n# Check Neo4j for completion\necho \"\" && echo \"2. Checking Neo4j for Mongke's task completion...\"\npython3 -c \"\nfrom neo4j import GraphDatabase\ndriver = GraphDatabase.driver('bolt://localhost:7687', auth=('neo4j', 'myStrongPassword123'))\nwith driver.session() as session:\n    result = session.run('MATCH (a:AgentState {name: \\\"mongke\\\"}) RETURN a.tasks_completed AS completed, a.status AS status')\n    record = result.single()\n    print(f'Mongke tasks completed: {record[\\\"completed\\\"] or 0}')\n    print(f'Mongke status: {record[\\\"status\\\"]}')\ndriver.close()\n\" 2>&1\n\n# Check workspace for result\necho \"\" && echo \"3. Checking Mongke workspace for research result...\"\nls -lt /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/mongke/workspace/*.md 2>/dev/null | head -3\n\n# Show the research result\necho \"\" && echo \"4. Research Result:\"\ncat /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/mongke/workspace/task-*.md 2>/dev/null | tail -50"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":413614,"output":598,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":414212,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772583440472}}
{"type":"message","id":"a03c6e7b","parentId":"7292bf96","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:17:39.910Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c649d7288c314e5e965b06be","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Testing Mongke: Prompt Injection Sandbox Research ===\n\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\n\n1. Sending research task to Mongke via direct-execute.py...\n=== Direct Task Execution ===\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections. ...\nClassification: complex → temujin\n  Executing with temujin...\n\n📋 Processing task: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for...\n  Status: executing → /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/direct-1772583456.executing.md\n  🤖 Executing with LLM...\n  ✓ Result saved: /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/workspace/task-1772583456.md\n✓ Task completed: /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/direct-1772583456.completed.done.md\n  ✓ Task completed\n\n✓ Execution complete: True\n\n2. Checking Neo4j for Mongke's task completion...\nMongke tasks completed: 0\nMongke status: running\n\n3. Checking Mongke workspace for research result...\nzsh:31: no matches found: /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/mongke/workspace/*.md\n\n4. Research Result:\nzsh:35: no matches found: /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/mongke/workspace/task-*.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3511,"aggregated":"=== Testing Mongke: Prompt Injection Sandbox Research ===\n\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\n\n1. Sending research task to Mongke via direct-execute.py...\n=== Direct Task Execution ===\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections. ...\nClassification: complex → temujin\n  Executing with temujin...\n\n📋 Processing task: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for...\n  Status: executing → /U