{"type":"message","id":"87421527","parentId":"bc6fef18","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:21:34.846Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1012df7348944c648d350cb8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Testing Kublai's Routing ===\n\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\n\n=== Kublai Task Router ===\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections...\n\nKublai's Decision:\n  Destination: jochi\n  Complexity: complex\n  Reasoning: Kublai routed to jochi based on task analysis\n\nAgent Scores: {'temujin': 4, 'mongke': 7, 'chagatai': 0, 'jochi': 4, 'ogedei': 0}\n\nFull routing decision:\n{\n  \"task\": \"Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\",\n  \"routed_by\": \"kublai\",\n  \"destination\": \"jochi\",\n  \"best_agent\": \"mongke\",\n  \"best_score\": 7,\n  \"complexity\": \"complex\",\n  \"scores\": {\n    \"temujin\": 4,\n    \"mongke\": 7,\n    \"chagatai\": 0,\n    \"jochi\": 4,\n    \"ogedei\": 0\n  },\n  \"reasoning\": \"Kublai routed to jochi based on task analysis\",\n  \"priority\": \"normal\",\n  \"routed_at\": \"2026-03-03T19:21:34.833922\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"=== Testing Kublai's Routing ===\n\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\n\n=== Kublai Task Router ===\nTask: Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections...\n\nKublai's Decision:\n  Destination: jochi\n  Complexity: complex\n  Reasoning: Kublai routed to jochi based on task analysis\n\nAgent Scores: {'temujin': 4, 'mongke': 7, 'chagatai': 0, 'jochi': 4, 'ogedei': 0}\n\nFull routing decision:\n{\n  \"task\": \"Research how to create a sandbox for testing LLM prompts for prompt injections\",\n  \"routed_by\": \"kublai\",\n  \"destination\": \"jochi\",\n  \"best_agent\": \"mongke\",\n  \"best_score\": 7,\n  \"comp