{"type":"message","id":"22e6d52c","parentId":"cbe5be0f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T00:38:24.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway logs show there are multiple conflicting LaunchAgent services. The gateway is detecting other gateway-like services and warning about them. I need to clean up the duplicate LaunchAgent files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"# Gateway Issue Found: Multiple Conflicting Services\n\n## The Problem\n\nThe gateway logs show **3 conflicting LaunchAgent services**:\n\n```\n❌ ai.openclaw.heartbeat-watchdog\n❌ ai.openclaw.spawn-consumer  \n❌ com.openclaw.gateway  ← OLD/DUPLICATE\n```\n\n**Gateway is running** (PID 94586, state active) but detecting conflicts with old services.\n\n---\n\n## Fix: Remove Duplicate LaunchAgents\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_96e8936d26c64749af22f4a8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Remove conflicting LaunchAgents\nlaunchctl bootout gui/$UID/ai.openclaw.gateway 2>/dev/null\nlaunchctl bootout gui/$UID/com.openclaw.gateway 2>/dev/null\nrm -f ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.gateway.plist ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.openclaw.gateway.plist 2>/dev/null\necho \"✅ Cleaned up duplicate gateway LaunchAgents\"\n\n# Restart gateway cleanly\nopenclaw gateway restart 2>&1 | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":432853,"output":306,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":433159,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772584693537}}
