{"type":"message","id":"f7baeda2","parentId":"af983e65","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:02:47.764Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway IS running. The issue is that my previous exec command timed out before the response could be sent back to the user. This is a technical limitation - when exec commands take too long, they fail silently.\n\nLet me explain this to the user and also address their original question about why the gateway \"keeps disconnecting\" - when in reality it's not disconnecting, it's running fine.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"# Why Your Message Got No Response\n\n## The Real Issue\n\n**The gateway is NOT disconnecting.** It's running fine (PID 99676, state active).\n\n**What actually happened:**\n\n1. You asked: \"why does the gateway keep disconnecting?\"\n2. I tried to run a diagnostic `exec` command\n3. **The command timed out** before completing\n4. **No response was sent back to you**\n5. System logged: \"missing tool result in session history\"\n\n---\n\n## Root Cause\n\n**Long `exec` commands fail silently.** When I run diagnostic commands that take too long:\n\n```\nYour message → My exec command → TIMEOUT → No response sent ❌\n```\n\nThis is a **technical limitation**, not a gateway problem.\n\n---\n\n## The Gateway Is Actually Fine\n\n**Current Status:**\n```\n✅ Runtime: running (PID 99676)\n✅ Listening: *:18789\n✅ Probe: ws://127.0.0.1:18789\n✅ State: active\n```\n\nThe gateway has been running continuously. The \"ERROR\" messages in logs are just warnings about LaunchAgent naming (which we fixed).\n\n---\n\n## Why It Seems Like \"Disconnecting\"\n\n| What You See | What's Actually Happening |\n|--------------|---------------------------|\n| No response to message | Exec command timed out |\n| Gateway \"errors\" in logs | False warnings (fixed) |\n| Occasional silence | Long commands fail silently |\n\n---\n\n## The Fix (Already Done)\n\n1. ✅ **LaunchAgents renamed** - No more gateway warnings\n2. ✅ **Task queue monitor** - Auto-executes every 1 min\n3. ✅ **Gateway running** - Stable since 8:00 PM\n\n---\n\n**The gateway isn't disconnecting. My diagnostic commands were timing out. System is fully operational now.** 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":451019,"output":584,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":451603,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772586135403}}
