{"type":"message","id":"385d7329","parentId":"9d5f8f5a","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:06:59.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The gateway LaunchAgent plist is missing but the LaunchAgent is still loaded. This is causing the gateway to restart periodically because:\n\n1. The LaunchAgent is loaded but has no plist file\n2. OpenClaw is trying to manage it but the config is \"out of date or non-standard\"\n3. The recommendation is to clear it with `launchctl bootout`\n\nThe fix is to:\n1. Boot out the broken LaunchAgent\n2. Let OpenClaw recreate it properly, OR\n3. Recreate the plist manually\n\nLet me fix this properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d8e193da07a74a6383e4c4dd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Fix the broken LaunchAgent\necho \"=== Fixing Gateway LaunchAgent ===\" && launchctl bootout gui/$UID/ai.openclaw.gateway 2>&1 && echo \"✅ Booted out broken LaunchAgent\" && sleep 2 && openclaw gateway restart 2>&1 | head -5 && sleep 3 && openclaw gateway status 2>&1 | grep -E \"Runtime:|Listening\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":455282,"output":361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":455643,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772586412312}}
