{"type":"message","id":"43196625","parentId":"6c5e0516","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:08:57.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is experiencing gateway crashes/disconnects. Based on my investigation, I found:\n\n1. The LaunchAgent plist is missing but the service is still registered\n2. The gateway keeps restarting (code 1012 \"service restart\" in logs)\n3. There's a PATH configuration issue\n\nThe exec commands keep timing out, which is preventing me from fixing this. Let me try a simpler, more direct approach with shorter commands.\n\nThe core issue seems to be:\n1. LaunchAgent plist is cached but file is missing\n2. Gateway is restarting every ~15 seconds\n3. Need to properly reinstall the gateway LaunchAgent\n\nLet me try a simpler fix approach.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_864b3c70b6af4c1facab918f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway stop"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":455521,"output":320,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":455841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772586528147}}
