{"type":"message","id":"e6ca0cda","parentId":"b8bef158","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:09:40.118Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"e17b8dca-89af-4993-98d6-8d9f6a145d7d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"sender\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 20:09 EST] the gateway keeps crashing. don't try to fix it yet, just tell me what's going on"}],"timestamp":1772586580107}}
{"type":"message","id":"e53a0fdf","parentId":"e6ca0cda","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:09:55.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to explain what's happening with the gateway, not try to fix it. Let me analyze what I've observed:\n\n1. The gateway LaunchAgent plist is missing/corrupted\n2. The LaunchAgent has been restarted multiple times\n3. There are warnings about PATH not being set\n4. The LaunchAgent label is cached but plist is missing\n5. Multiple restarts happening every ~15 seconds (code 1012 = service restart)\n\nLet me provide a clear explanation without trying to fix it.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"# What's Happening With The Gateway\n\n## Root Cause\n\n**The LaunchAgent plist file is MISSING but the LaunchAgent is still registered.**\n\nFrom the logs:\n```\nLaunchAgent label cached but plist missing.\nService config issue: Gateway service PATH is not set.\n```\n\n## What This Means\n\n1. **LaunchAgent Registration is Broken**\n   - LaunchAgent `ai.openclaw.gateway` is registered in launchd\n   - But the plist file (`~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.gateway.plist`) doesn't exist\n   - LaunchAgent keeps trying to restart but fails\n\n2. **Gateway is Crash-Restarting**\n   ```\n   webchat disconnected code=1012 reason=service restart\n   ```\n   - Code 1012 = service restart\n   - Happens every ~15 seconds\n   - Gateway starts → crashes → restarts → repeats\n\n3. **PATH Environment Variable Missing**\n   ```\n   Service config issue: Gateway service PATH is not set\n   ```\n   - The LaunchAgent doesn't have a proper PATH environment variable\n   - Gateway can't find node/npm binaries\n   - Crashes on startup\n\n## Why This Happened\n\nWhen I renamed the other LaunchAgents (`ai.openclaw.*` → `com.kurultai.agent.*`), something corrupted the gateway LaunchAgent registration. The plist file got deleted but the LaunchAgent stayed registered in launchd.\n\n## Current State\n\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| LaunchAgent | ❌ Registered but plist missing |\n| Gateway Process | ❌ Crash-restarting every 15s |\n| WebSocket | ❌ Disconnecting code=1012 |\n| PATH | ❌ Not configured |\n\n## What Needs To Happen\n\n1. Boot out the broken LaunchAgent\n2. Recreate the plist file with proper PATH\n3. Reload the LaunchAgent\n4. Restart gateway\n\n**But you said don't fix it yet, so I'm just reporting the issue.** The gateway will keep crash-restarting until the LaunchAgent is properly recreated."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":455749,"output":674,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":456423,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772586580114}}
{"type":"message","id":"7764e9be","parentId":"e53a0fdf","timestamp":"2026-03-04T01:09:55.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# What's Happening With The Gateway\n\n## Root Cause\n\n**The LaunchAgent plist file is MISSING but the LaunchAgent is still registered.**\n\nFrom the logs:\n```\nLaunchAgent label cached but plist missing.\nService config issue: Gateway service PATH is not set.\n```\n\n## What This Means\n\n1. **LaunchAgent Registration is Broken**\n   - LaunchAgent `ai.openclaw.gateway` is registered in launchd\n   - But the plist file (`~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.gateway.plist`) doesn't exist\n   - LaunchAgent keeps trying to restart but fails\n\n2. **Gateway is Crash-Restarting**\n   ```\n   webchat disconnected code=1012 reason=service restart\n   ```\n   - Code 1012 = service restart\n   - Happens every ~15 seconds\n   - Gateway starts → crashes → restarts → repeats\n\n3. **PATH Environment Variable Missing**\n   ```\n   Service config issue: Gateway service PATH is not set\n   ```\n   - The LaunchAgent doesn't have a proper PATH environment variable\n   - Gateway can't find node/npm binaries\n   - Crashes on startup\n\n## Why This Happened\n\nWhen I renamed the other LaunchAgents (`ai.openclaw.*` → `com.kurultai.agent.*`), something corrupted the gateway LaunchAgent registration. The plist file got deleted but the LaunchAgent stayed registered in launchd.\n\n## Current State\n\n| Component | Status |\n|-----------|--------|\n| LaunchAgent | ❌ Registered but plist missing |\n| Gateway Process | ❌ Crash-restarting every 15s |\n| WebSocket | ❌ Disconnecting code=1012 |\n| PATH | ❌ Not configured |\n\n## What Needs To Happen\n\n1. Boot out the broken LaunchAgent\n2. Recreate the plist file with proper PATH\n3. Reload the LaunchAgent\n4. Restart gateway\n\n**But you said don't fix it yet, so I'm just reporting the issue.** The gateway will keep crash-restarting until the LaunchAgent is properly recreated."}],"api":"o